<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>660</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yī qǐ wán chéng dà shǐ mìng 迦南660</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de dīng níng zhǔ de fēn fù, ràng wàn mín dōu lái zuò wǒ zhǔ mén tú.
 yī yàng de dà shǐ mìng yī qǐ lái wán chéng. zǒu biàn shén zhōu de nán běi xī dōng,
 yì xiàng yuè lái yuè qīng xī. dào lù yuè lái yuè guāng míng.
 féi wò fēng yú de tǔ de shàng, yào yǒu dà de shōu chéng.
 shén de wù dāng guī gěi shén, shèng jīng yǐn dǎo wǒ men qián xíng.
 wǒ men yī qǐ wǒ men yī qǐ wán chéng dà shǐ mìng.</lyrics>
</song>